{"tid":110312,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"（香港仔飲評）積熱清 VS 清熱酷","createTime":"2017-02-06T14:48:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-06T16:02:22.000Z","uid":23479,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"61a8d0d1de97ee6f3c2ea044a82b27152f2c80ee","tid":110312,"uid":23479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T14:48:48.000Z","msg":"今日見熱氣，身體毒左幾日，身為傳統香港人，所以決定落去買野清熱<br />\n今日買咗：<br />\n積熱清<br />\n清熱酷<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">合共幾十蚊</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6hbl15ra\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6hbl15ra&h=59f3c0ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">左面係積熱清，長方形包裝，而右面係清熱酷，正方形包裝</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/01ejha5u\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F01ejha5u&h=42b36151&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">睇成份應該係積熱清勁啲，因為清熱酷只得白茅根係涼性，而積熱清除左白茅根外，仲有蘆薈根、金銀花、石斛、綠茶提取物都係涼性，寒底既人就要小心，特別係金銀花！</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/kyrfa0qx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fkyrfa0qx&h=061cfe47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n總括而言︰積熱清比較抵買，兩者價錢只係相差五蚊左右"},{"pid":"6c4cedc0e6547144f4e38218b64836886359d5a7","tid":110312,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:10:00.000Z","msg":"清熱酷味道好啲<br />\n利申熱氣一係啤酒一係廿四味"},{"pid":"2c4e9d23419455e56a13bcbd9d0bd5530e9e9c26","tid":110312,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:11:18.000Z","msg":"廿四is the best"},{"pid":"1e42df88fa827d7ae47cf4eb0d4fea0b6b23bb72","tid":110312,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:13:32.000Z","msg":"積熱清勁好多"},{"pid":"1ed14256cdbe806dd2d8d11075f9e9a604031e1e","tid":110312,"uid":23479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:16:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>清熱酷味道好啲<br />\n利申熱氣一係啤酒一係廿四味</blockquote><br />\n積熱清有羅漢果同果皮味，唔係咁多人慣"},{"pid":"a9ea73f4ad27625e2e386a7ab5debaaf26b60f23","tid":110312,"uid":23479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:17:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>清熱酷味道好啲<br />\n利申熱氣一係啤酒一係廿四味</blockquote><br />\n積熱清有羅漢果同果皮味，唔係咁多人慣</blockquote><br />\n陳皮先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f8fca34daf0bae58ae6fda570f09d238c81e686","tid":110312,"uid":74084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:18:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>清熱酷味道好啲<br />\n利申熱氣一係啤酒一係廿四味</blockquote><br />\n而家好多間啲廿四味都無料到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無邊間好介紹？"},{"pid":"a9d4f5fef04ff6a4f92e837e7fa755bbea52175b","tid":110312,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:20:45.000Z","msg":"積熱清幾錢盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一盒入面有幾包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"567fc0ff1f582f5e9ae4ea79c6dc9c59f8a1e0a2","tid":110312,"uid":42009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:25:08.000Z","msg":"淨係飲過積熱清，<br />\n都幾ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f1cc5978ef63ab8b05884da23a852cfa1b0828","tid":110312,"uid":23479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:33:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>積熱清幾錢盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一盒入面有幾包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我買大約$25 四包"},{"pid":"45f4e9afdf21796a4b965d12bfd501916afd33dd","tid":110312,"uid":8264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:47:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0627bd9a6b56eb1b16717f30a902e790a47bb3c2","tid":110312,"uid":61678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:51:44.000Z","msg":"飲開支裝 沖係咪差唔多味 百佳有得買？"},{"pid":"894b1eddb49d420001d68734e1b8dd8abcfa3058","tid":110312,"uid":23479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T16:02:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飲開支裝 沖係咪差唔多味 百佳有得買？</blockquote><br />\n我係百佳買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />放到好鬼鼠"}]}